{"tid":21516,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"EXO Lay奪大獎謝詞被轟狂妄 「拿獎的感覺真是爽。」","createTime":"2016-12-04T01:55:37.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T05:44:19.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c3434d49d95fef4e0f251fac26d04f7280c0a42c","tid":21516,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T01:55:37.000Z","msg":"黎明（Leon）一向與韓國藝能界有淵源，前晚他現身「MAMA亞洲音樂大獎」擔任壓軸頒獎嘉賓，頒獎給人氣男團EXO，在後台就吸引朴寶劍、秀智及劉亞仁集郵。而EXO內地成員Lay發表得獎感受時，稱希望「前浪永遠站在最高的山頂上」，惹來外界批評他太狂妄。 <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20161204/small/04ec1p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161204%2Fsmall%2F04ec1p1.jpg&h=1abb8e55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓國年度「MAMA亞洲音樂大獎」前晚在亞博館舉行，人氣韓星如李秉憲、秀智、EXO、車勝元、少女時代隊長泰妍等聚首一堂，吸引大批韓迷撐場。大會去年找了周潤發做壓軸頒獎嘉賓，今年由黎明接棒，頒獎給奪得年度專輯獎的EXO。 <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20161204/small/04ec1p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161204%2Fsmall%2F04ec1p2.jpg&h=943489b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nEXO憑着《EX'ACT》連續四年獲得年度專輯獎，隊長Suho從Leon手上領獎，他90度恭敬鞠躬，而世勛發表得獎感受時表示：「以後會帶畀大家更好面貌，多謝大家！」另一內地成員Lay則以普通話說：「咱們中國有一句話叫做『長江後浪推前浪』，我希望EXO用自己的努力改寫這後半句話，前浪永遠站在最高的山頂上。」加上之前他得獎時曾霸氣表示：「拿獎的感覺真是爽。」等，結果引來網民批評太狂妄，覺得他不尊重長輩，更叫他不要拖累其他隊友。 <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20161204/small/04ec1p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161204%2Fsmall%2F04ec1p3.jpg&h=589e8928&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樂迷催Quincy走<br />\n<br />\n此外，大會請來曾與米高積遜（Michael Jackson）合作的美國老牌音樂人Quincy Jones擔任頒獎嘉賓，卻發生不快事件。當台上播放以往得獎片段，預告即將頒發大獎時，樂迷卻太心急，未有理會Quincy講話已接近尾聲，即大嗌「Bye」，似想催促他快回後台，令一班得獎者可以早點捧獎，不過Quincy沒有即刻返入後台，反而落台時回敬了一句「shut up」才離開。"},{"pid":"a6cea3988d58c9903ba435ce98bef1901abb0c91","tid":21516,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T02:00:08.000Z","msg":"韓狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6303b21ecb3dfe0401aa3e0d1ec46d4fd0f5cb73","tid":21516,"uid":53207,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T02:12:29.000Z","msg":"大陸lay冇改錯名<br />\n上年段rap重未柒夠<br />\n今年重黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就是爽！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"accba4f558d7b69103c8e77419dbd33e9e4ccac0","tid":21516,"uid":29863,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T02:31:33.000Z","msg":"就是爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e39730acaff6551d4e6837396afd3ea00c0e7d94","tid":21516,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T02:41:41.000Z","msg":"其實無咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49bc835887e8b96d634e16d6bb8bbf59985a90bd","tid":21516,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:06:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實無咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問題係出自韓狗把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b803b661e6628ef802c9cce6c9479057c765c85b","tid":21516,"uid":35160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:18:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實無咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你睇條片 佢個樣同語氣就會覺得好有問題"},{"pid":"74dfdcbc47122b79f5a72eba85b73aa3b161af96","tid":21516,"uid":15479,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:39:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實無咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nexo係度係原罪黎 講乜都比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c9d6d268